# Git branch naming

Working branches: `<type>/<short-description>` (`feat`/`fix`/`chore`/`refactor`/`docs`/`test`/`ci`/`build`/`perf`). Single trunk: `main` is the only long-lived branch; short-lived `release/*` version branches carry hotfixes for older releases; `claude/*` is reserved for AI web sessions. Enforced by `.husky/pre-push` (owner: **[code-quality-guard](../skills/code-quality-guard/SKILL.md)**).
